程序包 com.example.qrconnect

类 Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.qrconnect.Event
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
public class Event extends Object implements Serializable
The Event class defines an event. Contains details such as title, date, time, location, capacity, announcement, and associated QR codes.

    • Event

      public Event(String eventTitle, Calendar date, Calendar time, String location, Integer capacity, String description, String checkInQRCodeImageUrl, String promoQRCodeImageUrl, String eventId, String hostId, HashMap<String,Long> attendeeListIdToCheckInTimes, HashMap<String,String> attendeeListIdToName, HashMap<String,String> attendeeListIdToLocation, HashMap<String,String> signupUserIdToName)
      Constructs an Event object with the specified details.
      参数:
      eventTitle - the title of an event.
      time - the time of an event.
      location - the location of an event.
      capacity - the capacity of an event.
      description - the announcement of an event.
      checkInQRCodeImageUrl - the id of the QR code of an event.
      promoQRCodeImageUrl - the id of the promotion QR code of an event.
      eventId - the id of an event.
      hostId - the id of an event organizer.
      attendeeListIdToCheckInTimes - the hashMap with userId and check-in#.
